<span class='tline' id='l7' data-llen='155:181'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0084', 'WYG', '095-1a' );" name="095-1a" class="pb">[095-1a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l8' data-llen='181:189'>欽定四庫全書</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l9' data-llen='189:198'>　禮書卷九十六</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l10' data-llen='198:219'>　　　　　　　　　　　　宋　陳祥道　撰</span><br/>
<span class='tline' id='l11' data-llen='219:245'><a onclick="displayPageImage('KR1d0084', 'WYG', '095-2a' );" name="095-2a" class="pb">[095-2a] <img width="20"  src="/static/img/kanseki-5.png"/></a></span><br/>
